This is a video that I made a while back. The videos portrays the Gemini 3 missions and is a part of my KSP Cinematic show.

I really hope that you enjoy the video. Please leave a comment and subscribe if you like what you see, because more is coming!

Link to video: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_npFEpSQ8Cg
This is amazing dude! A sub from me. Is that the stock NovaPunch rocket you used?
No, it is the Gemini/mercury Mod pack at Spaceport;-) You can find it here: http://kerbalspaceprogram.com/gemini-and-mercury-frizzank-aeronautical-space-administration-fasa/
